15. Create a PHP program to compute the sum of the digits of a number.



<?php  
$number = 1234;   
$sum = 0;  
while ($number > 0) {  
    $digit = $number % 10;    
    $sum += $digit;           
    $number = (int)($number / 10);   
}  
echo "Sum of digits is: " . $sum;  
?>  output:Sum of digits is: 10
